title: $720 Room Available for Rent in Safe Area (Palo Alto)
description:
Hi there,
I'm looking for a new roommate to move into a 3-bedroom, 2-bath apartment in North Berkeley starting June 1st. You’ll have your own private bathroom and a bedroom in a comfortable, well-located apartment.

Apartment Details:

Located just a few minutes from North Berkeley BART, major bus lines, restaurants, and Target.

Rent: $1,700/month plus split utilities and internet.

Shared living area is fully furnished, including a living room, dining area, and fully equipped kitchen.

Your bedroom has an attached private bathroom.

Free street parking and coin-operated laundry on-site.

About Me:
I work in the nonprofit sector and enjoy walks and discovering new coffee shops. I keep a clean and friendly home, and I’m looking for a roommate who is respectful, tidy, and easygoing.

If you're interested, please send me a message and tell me a bit about yourself. Looking forward to hearing from you!
